{"id": "1480695722461368461", "channel_id": "1480695722461368461", "author_id": "1160510535670968330", "author_name": "yeriko703", "content": "You can lose tentacle but you don't care if you lose all tentacle in \"Raging Waves\", and after i thinking \"Image if we can have literaly 0 tentacle\" i mean if enemy in ch4 can lose all tentacle why we can't?\n\nAnd now we here, my suggestion is punish if at the end of the turn you have only 1 tentacle and tentacle in red posse(Raging Waves) you lose this tentacle and need wait one turn before can use other options. Raging Waves -> Vortice exalt -> You have only one tentacle at the end of the turn -> You don't have ANY tentacle at this turn -> You have one tentacle \n\nPlay smarter Keeper! <:point:1356053112292511815>\n\nI know it sounds really stuffy, but I'd like to see it at least as an opponent. \"You lose one tentacle this turn. If you only have one tentacle, you lose the ability to interact with tentacles for one turn.\" <:please:1356053110375714817>", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T22:36:10.231000+00:00", "thread_id": "1480695722461368461", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-09T22:38:58.499000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "✖️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1480695722662826055", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 213796, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1480695722461368461/1480695722662826055/image.png?ex=69fb199a&is=69f9c81a&hm=56dafc0734ba24caf7ef6c61065abe44a39d332ddf14ddb34b01aa23eac976f6&"}, {"id": "1480695723224993902", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 23942, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1480695722461368461/1480695723224993902/image.png?ex=69fb199a&is=69f9c81a&hm=83fc62f7e3093bd15881c5a6048c6c691453dd8e30f0adc980c0c01db00be365&"}]}
